game.name: Princesses Graduation Party Night
game.description:
Today is a big day for these four beautiful princesses who have earned their graduation degree. This creates a reason to celebrate and have fun together. So they have planned to organize a party at their home tonight. The problem is that they have multiple things to do so they hired you as their personal fashion designer. Would you accept this challenge? Join Princess Graduation Party Night and be prepared to guide them to pick up the coolest looks for this evening!
There are multiple choices of luxurious and chick outfits to choose from in this one of the best HTML5 dressing games for girls. Start with the princess that you see on the left side of the screen! Dress up Cinderella with an off-shoulder pink midi tulle outfit and pair it with a headband with pink flowers, a pair of nude sandals and a cupcake shaped handbag! Make sure to style her hair with the awesome curls and select the silver eye shadow and pink lipstick for her. 
Belle loves to be dressed up with a red fitted mini outfit with bell sleeves along with a matching clutch and a golden necklace. Give her a nice makeover with the help of big eye lashes, red lips and a vintage hairstyle! A white lace top combined with a purple dress, a curly haircut, statement jewelry and a pair of black color sandals. Do not forget to give her nude lips, black eye shadow and glittery eye shadow. A wrapped golden outfit with a combination of black and gold accessories will suit the personality of Ariel. Enjoy more dress up challenges for free online on atmegame.com!
